snippet.textDisplay:
I really appreciate that the WHO understands that sticking a country's name next to the Variant will automatically result in fantastically racist opinions from idiots.

Also I would like to know which of the variants; P1, B1351, B1617, B117
Correspond to which of the names Alpha, Beta, Gamma, Delta, Lambda and Mu variants circling around in the news.

Ps: please ban the commenters spreading misinformation in the comment section. It's makes it harder for concerned individuals who to trust despite how insane the claims that are made.
